snippet.title: Seekers of Skyveil | Play Now during Steam Next Fest
snippet.description:
PLAY NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2402420/Seekers_of_Skyveil/

MOBA + EXTRACTION. Team-based PvPvE with top-down combat, where players battle for powerful loot against rivals. Gear up, make a plan, and set a course for Skyveil. Stealthy treasure runs explode into multi-team PvP chaos in an instant. Extract with your riches—or lose it all.
